    exampleReading: 'Selecting Taurus: The tool displays a 2026 theme of building stability through adaptability. Growth area focuses on embracing change while maintaining core values. Key challenge involves balancing comfort with necessary transformation. Opportunity highlights financial or career advancement. Favorable months include April, June, and October, displayed as badge buttons.',
